{"type":"article","id":13393,"title":"大陆废青被逼急啦，福建宁德上千村民堵路并与警察冲突","uid":27874,"topics":[5262],"contents":"大陆废青的出处：<a href=\"https://www.pincong.rocks/article/3188\">https://www.pincong.rocks/article/3188</a><br>\n<br>\n懒得看原链接的，看下面从微博上扒下来的精髓<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/WTEDTjO.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WTEDTjO.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/WTEDTjO.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n===下面突开正题===<br>\n<br>\n原文链接：<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/gb/20/1/30/n11831338.htm\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/gb/20/1/30/n11831338.htm</a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/WZN7F5h.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WZN7F5h.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/WZN7F5h.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<i>福建千人堵路 大陆爆首个涉疫情警民冲突<br>\n<br>\n【大纪元2020年01月30日讯】（大纪元记者周慧心综合报导）<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/gb/tag/%E6%96%B0%E5%9E%8B%E5%86%A0%E7%8A%B6%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新型冠状病毒</a>肺炎疫情愈发严峻，官方的强制<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/gb/tag/%E9%9A%94%E7%A6%BB.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">隔离</a>引发民众不满，福建28日有上千人堵路抗议，爆发首个涉及疫情的警民激烈冲突。</i><br>\n<br>\n<i>有网民在twitter上发出视频，显示有上千名民众堵住村内道路，与警方爆发冲突期间，有人不时向警方投掷杂物。防暴警员手持盾牌。</i><br>\n<br>\n<i>中国大陆社交平台上转载的讯息显示，这次发生警民冲突的是<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/gb/tag/%E7%A6%8F%E5%BB%BA%E5%AE%81%E5%BE%B7.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">福建宁德</a>市霞浦县村民，原因是“不满<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/gb/tag/%E6%96%B0%E5%9E%8B%E5%86%A0%E7%8A%B6%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新型冠状病毒</a>疫情的<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/gb/tag/%E9%9A%94%E7%A6%BB.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">隔离</a>中心，过于接近民宅”，忧心被感染，愤而堵路，且向员警投掷木板、座椅等杂物，警方将示威者抬走。······</i><br>\n<br>\n===华丽的分